overview: Marina and Joaquín are two strangers who meet on the outskirts of an engagement party and discover that they have one thing in common: they are having a horrible time and they want to escape. Marina has had intimate photographs shown in the middle of the event, and Joaquín has loose ends with the hosts. Together they must find the best way to get ahead: go for tacos.
tagline: A couple of strangers find something in common: it's a terrible night for both of them.
title: Tacomplicado
